race.comment: ZIPPING URBAN (6) got around the 366m at Capalaba to take a Grade 5 in a swift 19.81 for a neck win. Smart win latest and looks a key chance again here. UNRULY BOY (2) finished in the minors last time but only a few starts back broke the clock when winning over 457m at this track, taking a OPEN in a flying 25.34. Top win three back and can measure up again. ZIPPING LIPA (4) has a strong record this track and trip with four wins and three placings from 10 starts. Scored by 2.5 lengths last time (25.39) in a Restricted WIN over 457m at this track. Can hit the frame with the right run. SPEED HOLES (8) comes under notice as a past winner at this course and distance.
